142726.name: Agriculture (GHG Emissions, CAIT)
142726.description: Greenhouse gas emissions from agriculture, measured in tonnes of carbon dioxide-equivalents.
142726.datasetName: GHG Emissions by Country and Sector (CAIT)
142726.s_name: GHG Emissions by Country and Sector (CAIT)

source.name: GHG Emissions by Country and Sector (CAIT)
source.dataPublishedBy: CAIT Climate Data Explorer via. Climate Watch
source.additionalInfo:
Total greenhouse gas emissions are measured in tonnes of carbon dioxide equivalents (COe), based on 100-year global warming potential factors for non-CO gases.

This data is published by country and sector from the CAIT Climate Data Explorer, and downloaded from the Climate Watch Portal. Available here: https://www.climatewatchdata.org/data-explorer/historical-emissions
